247
00:13:50,025 --> 00:13:53,095
What's he doin?
- That ain't Wotagei.

248
00:13:53,095 --> 00:13:54,095
What's he doin!?

249
00:13:54,560 --> 00:13:56,640
This ain't Wotagei.

250
00:13:57,520 --> 00:14:00,300
He's not doing it at all.

251
00:14:00,420 --> 00:14:02,080
People notice him, right?

252
00:14:02,420 --> 00:14:07,140
Everyone's looking at the weirdo.

253
00:14:07,760 --> 00:14:08,600
Makes sense.

254
00:14:09,960 --> 00:14:11,180
They're scared.

255
00:14:11,180 --> 00:14:14,300
Maybe the uncomfortable people will tweet something.

256
00:14:14,880 --> 00:14:16,680
You're sluggish.

257
00:14:19,040 --> 00:14:21,940
What is that? What are you doin?

258
00:14:22,980 --> 00:14:23,980
Wotagei.

259
00:14:24,155 --> 00:14:25,465
I don't know Wotagei.

260
00:14:25,920 --> 00:14:28,200
Is it faster?
- Faster.

261
00:14:28,400 --> 00:14:30,140
Faster?
- Yeah.

262
00:14:30,560 --> 00:14:31,800
Faster?

263
00:14:37,820 --> 00:14:41,160
The speed's gone up.
- Nice, nice. It's cleaner.

264
00:14:41,520 --> 00:14:43,080
No tweets?

265
00:14:43,180 --> 00:14:44,900
But people are watching.

266
00:14:45,160 --> 00:14:47,320
The people around you are watching.

267
00:14:47,660 --> 00:14:49,840
This is tough. This is tough.

268
00:14:50,540 --> 00:14:51,780
This is tough.

269
00:14:52,875 --> 00:14:55,835
Maybe they're foreigners.
- Maybe.

270
00:14:55,840 --> 00:14:57,580
